# Stage 5.5: Legacy Endpoints (Retired)
# These endpoints return HTTP 410 Gone.
# All activation now uses Stage 4/5 device-based endpoints.
#
# Migration:
#   POST /api/license/activate  → Use POST /api/licence/activate (with deviceId)
#   POST /api/license/deactivate → Use POST /api/licence/deactivate (with deviceId)
#
# Active endpoints:
#   - POST /api/device/register
#   - POST /api/licence/activate
#   - POST /api/licence/refresh
#   - POST /api/licence/deactivate
#   - POST /api/licence/offline-challenge (subscriptions only)
#   - POST /api/licence/offline-refresh (subscriptions only)

